---
title: Southwestern Pork Fajitas with Tomato-Lime Salsa and Cheddar Cheese
description: Easy, fast and packed with flavour! Sweet peppers and onions pair perfectly with tender pork for a fun fajita meal that all comes together with our fabulous Southwest Spice Blend.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/fajitas-de-porc-a-la-mode-sud-ouest-313c7394.jpg
